Chapter 2:  Knebeln and Sklav

Despite their... odd emailing strategies, Knebeln and Sklav looked like an utterly professional affair.

Multiple studios to shoot in, a well stocked break room with lots of drinks and snacks,  a lounge to relax in between shoots, and plenty of helpful staff...

An almost exclusively male staff.
